  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-119fve5\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"SPrJ_Nxg\">缺爱，极致的缺爱。</p><p data-pid=\"37kR8WVN\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1992940719472672970\" data-highlight-split-type=\"head\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">和女性缺爱仅仅是99%和100%的区别不同，男性的缺爱是0%和1%——整个小男孩到青年的培养流程就是在抽干他感知爱的能力、打造“冷酷的战斗机器”的过程，一个听话的男孩必然会变成缺乏感情、低</span><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=734362240&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%88%B1%E5%95%86&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1992940719472672970\" data-highlight-split-type=\"none\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">爱商</span><svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1992940719472672970\" data-highlight-split-type=\"tail\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">的活尸。</span></p><p data-pid=\"dYuabwLy\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1994840936430204414\" data-highlight-split-type=\"head\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">小时候被教育受伤不能哭闹，必须承担责任，长大了又被要求隐忍沉稳，从父母那里得不到像样的</span><span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=734362240&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%BB%B7%E5%80%BC&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1994840936430204414\" data-highlight-split-type=\"none\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">情绪价值</span><svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span><span class=\"highlight-wrap other\" data-highlight-id=\"1994840936430204414\" data-highlight-split-type=\"tail\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">，同龄的同性之间又存在残酷的竞争，很难获取一个能八卦日常的朋友——至少我自己这么多年只遇见过两个。</span></p><p data-pid=\"DYRIvTgh\">不开玩笑，<span class=\"highlight-wrap other has-comments\" data-highlight-id=\"1994840957946975929\" data-highlight-split-type=\"both\" data-highlight-id-extra=\"\">年轻男性获取爱和认可的唯一途径大概只有同龄女性了，但是偏偏这条路甚至比学业和事业更残酷，因为一张帅脸是不能靠努力取得的。男追女隔座山，大部分时候尝试接近同龄女性只会被对方默认为索取性价值然后被礼貌拒绝or一脚踢开——有没有可能男性也是只想要一个抱抱呢？没有人关心。</span></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
